{"lemma":"مَعْدُود","slug":"مَعْدُود","root":"ع.د.د","root_slug":"ع-د-د","root_link":"/words/roots/ع-د-د","pos":"ADJ","pos_camel":"adj","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"مَعْدُود","root":"عدد","pos":"N","occurrence_count":1},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["adj"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":3},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n28297"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%85%D9%8E%D8%B9%D9%92%D8%AF%D9%8F%D9%88%D8%AF"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"adj","gloss":"passive participle of عَدَّ (ʕadda)","tags":["form-of","participle","passive"]},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"counted, enumerated"},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"limited in number, a few","examples":[{"text":"وَقَالُوا لَن تَمَسَّنَا ٱلنَّارُ إِلَّا أَيَّامًا مَعْدُودَةً","english":"And they claim, “The Fire will not touch us except for a number of days.”"}]}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Derived from the passive participle of عَدَّ (ʕadda, “to count”)."},"ipa":["/maʕ.duːd/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n28297","headword_ar":"مَعْدُودٌ","root":"Ed","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"[meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Numbered, counted, reckoned,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"computed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"] is applied to any number, little or large; but"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maEoduwdaAtN","text_ar":"مَعْدُودَاتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"more particularly denotes few; and so does every pl. formed by the addition of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A","text_ar":"ا"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"t","text_ar":"ت"},{"kind":"text","text":", as"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"durayohimaAtN","text_ar":"دُرَيْهِمَاتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HamaAmaAtN","text_ar":"حَمَامَاتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; though it is allowable to use such a pl. to denote muchness. (Zj, TA.)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlA^ay~aAmu AlmaEoduwdaAtu","text_ar":"الاَيَّامُ المَعْدُودَاتُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The days called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ay~aAmu Alt~a$oriyqi","text_ar":"اَيَّامُ التَّشْرِيقِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, Mgh, O, Msb, K;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the three days next after the day of the sacrifice"},{"kind":"text","text":"[which is the tenth of Dhu-l-Hijjeh]; thus called because they are few. (TA.) And one also says"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"daraAhimu maEoduwdapN","text_ar":"دَرَاهِمُ مَعْدُودَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[lit."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Numbered,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"counted, dirhems"},{"kind":"text","text":"] as meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a few dirhems."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)"}],"source_refs":[]}]}}